        "subject": "搶答206",
        "content": "<p>206. 撰寫程式碼說明氣泡排序bubble sort如何提早結束執行。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nvoid bubble_sort(int arr[],int n){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;int i,j,temp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;int swap; //紀錄是否有交換&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;for(i=0,i&lt;n-1;i++){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;swap=0;//初始化swap&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;for(j=0;j&lt;n-i-1;j++){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if(arr[j]&gt;arr[j+1]){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;temp=arr[j];<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;arr[j]=arr[j+1];<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;arr[j+1]=temp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;swap=1; //標記有交換&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if(swap==0){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;break;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;} //如果沒有交換，表示順序已經好了，提前結束&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>在過程中發現swap=0代表沒有交換了，順序已排好，就可提早結束執行</p>",
